
'''Malaika Uwamahoro''' (wahoze ari '''Angel Uwamahoro''', yavutse 1990) ni umukinnyi wa filime wavukiye mu [[Rwanda]], kandi ni umusizi, umuririmbyi, ni umuntu ukunda guharanira ubutabera .<ref name="AN">http://amsterdamnews.com/news/2019/apr/18/miracle-rwanda-shows-power-faith-love-forgiveness/</ref> <ref name="For">https://www.forbesafrica.com/arts/2020/05/03/our-home-became-the-film-set-blankets-became-props-windows-became-locations/</ref> <ref name="MIR">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/malaika-uwamahoro-starring-miracle-rwanda</ref> Aba i Portland, Maine, muri [[Amerika]]. <ref name="F">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/uwamahoro-speak-forbes-2020-women-summit</ref>

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Uwamahoro yavukiye mu [[Rwanda]] mu 1990. Bitewe n’ibyabaye kuri Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi yakurikiyeho yo muri 1994 , nyina yahunganye na we muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]] aho yatuye imyaka irindwi, hanyuma ajya muri [[Amerika]] amaherezo mu 2001, agaruka mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/210551</ref> Yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse y’ubuhanzi mu masomo y’ikinamico muri kaminuza ya Fordham, mu mujyi wa New York.  <ref name="UN">https://news.un.org/en/story/2017/04/554942-learn-lessons-rwanda-says-un-chief-calling-future-tolerance-human-rights-all</ref>

== Umwuga ==

=== Filime ===
Yagaragaye muri filime ya Tomas Petkovski yo muri 2018, ''LoveLess Generation'' . <ref name="Lov">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt9098680/?ref_=m_nm_knf_t2</ref> Mubiganiro bya tereviziyo byakozwe muri uwo mwaka na Tola Olatunji bise, ''Yankee Hustle'', binagaragaramo Jide Kosoko, Uche Jombo, Kara Rainer n'abandi, akina nka "Princess". <ref name="Yan">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8883238/?ref_=m_nm_knf_i3</ref>

Muri 2019, yagaragaye muri filime iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa firime ukomoka muri Afuganisitani Atiq Rahimi, ''Our Lady of the Nile'' ( [[Igifaransa|Igifaransa:]] ''Notre-Dame du Nil'' ). <ref name="Our">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8690948/?ref_=m_nm_knf_i1</ref> <ref>https://www.planocritico.com/critica-nossa-senhora-do-nilo/</ref> <ref>https://variety.com/2019/film/reviews/film-review-our-lady-of-the-nile-1203325073/</ref> <ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/377814/</ref> <ref>https://www.broadwayworld.com/los-angeles/article/Drive-In-to-theOpening-Night-Films-from-Method-Fest-20200818</ref>  yongeye kugaragara mu ikinamico yo hanze ya Broadway na Leslie Lewis Sword na Edward Vilga bise,''Miracle in Rwanda'' . <ref>https://www.playbillplanocritico.com/article/miraclecritica-innossa-rwandasenhora-willdo-arrive-off-broadway-this-springnilo/</ref>   Kuri iyikiinamico, yatowe mu cyiciro cyiza cya ''Solo Performance'' muri VIV Award 2019. <ref>https://www.playbill.com/article/the-secret-life-of-bees-much-ado-about-nothing-lead-2019-audelcos-viv-award-nominations</ref>

=== Umuziki ===
Yagaragaye mu ndirimbo y'umuririmbyi wo mu Rwanda Mucyo, ''Stickin '2 you'', yakozwe na Eloi El. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/weekender/kigali-creatives-backstory-stickin-2-you</ref>

=== Ibisigo ===
Yakinnye ku munsi mpuzamahanga wo kwibuka Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu [[Rwanda]] mu 2017. <ref name="UN" /> Yamenyekanye nk'umwe mu bahanzi bitabiriye ibirori bya DanceAfrica 2019. <ref>https://bklyner.com/weekend-art-events-may-24-26/</ref> Muri 2020, mugihe cya guma mu rugo, bavugaga ko yanditse igisigo, ''I Don't Mind!'' . 

Yari umwe mu batanze ibiganiro batoranijwe kugira ngo bavugire mu nama y'abagore bayoboye Forbes Woman Africa 2020, yabereye i Durban, muri [[Afurika y'Epfo]].  <ref>https://mediaupdate.co.za/media/148105/2020-fwa-leading-women-summit-announces-its-speaker-line-up</ref>

